<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Jun1937"><font color="red">8 June 1937</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to C.P. Curran): [in-law&apos;s name O Brion? Byrne? Griffin?] These people would be ideal readers for <i>Work in Progress</i> but for the fact that they feel they could do so much better themselves if only they would take the trouble of so doing. After 15 years I was still tinkering away at it at 5 a.m. this morning. </div>
